{"tid":1437162,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[討論]有關於明天大埔遊山玩水 補習","createTime":"2019-08-09T12:48:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-09T17:39:48.000Z","uid":94771,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"009c0f6d62235572745cd4938ba0009502b45a52","tid":1437162,"uid":94771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T12:48:53.000Z","msg":"首先我地睇下個地型<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TicV37E.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTicV37E.png&h=f8ccd9c0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實大埔幾有特色<br />\n分開幾個區域 幾個區域好明顯係橋同橋之間連接<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YLeQS7e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYLeQS7e.png&h=0ff08738&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n你發現個地型如果比人襲擊 <strong>係好容易比人包圍</strong> 因為只要封佐橋同橋之間連接就會<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果比人襲擊就最好搵警署報案啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 依個警署重要係總區來 好大的<br />\n所以大家可以放心去總區報案 總區唔會唔夠警察的 點講都係警總<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Dde5G4L.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDde5G4L.jpg&h=5ba4da19&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n另一方面 右邊近吐露港公路有公園仔 個公園仔有回歸塔 昆蟲館 個草地又大 又可以放風爭 絕對係野餐的好去處 <br />\n<br />\n而想出返沙田的朋友都可以玩下單車 做埋運動<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實大埔重有好多野玩好多野食的 而且都幾多運動好去處 鐘意踢波的巴打有運了 大埔都有唔少足球場 希望大家玩得開開心心<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4223ddc48950e2e00c73b5f7ecf756c07d894ea5","tid":1437162,"uid":161436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T13:04:13.000Z","msg":"全部人一齊推返聽日大埔嘅post!!!<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95edb8a4ad6d0e101d30e15641ca645000b4da64","tid":1437162,"uid":94771,"like":0,"dislike":